* Truncate and ellipsify project/description text in report
* Email an export
* Mechanism to automatically update the version number

* Set up "queue" to replace tasks. Should be able to queue a task, and then take
  it off the queue, and in doing so, start the timer on that task.
* Queue should also show you what your day will look like if you attend to all
  the stuff you're supposed to be doing.
* Ability to add ticket number to activity, so that hours can be tracked for
  Almost Scrum.
